,Recommended,227780,27869619,"Posted: 27 November, 2016",all,Schrotflinte12,"This game is all about shooting monsters with awesome, big and destructive guns while you are walking through the beautiful landscapes of Ancient Egypt, Mayan Civilization, Persian Empire and Medieval Europe.The game features over 25 levels, where you can find a lot of secrets.Serious Sam is an old-school game, this means that you fight without cover against serious masses of enemies. There can be over 100+ enemies rushing towards you! To stop them, you get to fight with a minigun, a laser, a cannon and many more weapons!You can also choose to play with other players together or play against them in some serious deatmatch.Serious Sam Revolution merged the two original games The first Encounter and The second Encounter into one game. It also features more weapons, secrets, monsters and gamemodes.Positive:- Tons of enemies, weapons and levels.- Modding support.- Singleplay, co-op, versus modes.- Support for modern computers.- Still great graphics for such an old game.- 10h of serious destruction!- Leaderboards.- Ongoing support by the developers, though it's slow....aaannnddd it features both original games (Serious Sam TFE Classic and the Second Encounter Classic) too!Negative:- There are some bugs.- Multiplayer doesnt have many players.- Savegames are broken after each update. (You can still load them, you need to enable this in the options menu.)- Will probably still remain some time in early access...TL;DR:You fight monsters with big guns in a lot of levels. There's no cover, just you against them.Time to get SERIOUS!"
